{"tid":2181891,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"巴菲特旗下巴群宣佈入股日本五大商社各5％股份","createTime":"2020-08-31T02:35:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T05:12:19.000Z","uid":28765,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b979f47d768b9977f64461d2220b6cf804e431b0","tid":2181891,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T02:35:52.000Z","msg":"「股神」巴菲特（Warren Buffett）旗下控股公司「波克夏海瑟威」（Berkshire Hathaway）30日宣佈，在過去12個月內，已收購日本5大商社伊藤忠商事、丸紅、三菱商事、三井物產、住友商事各超過5%的股份，未來還可能進一步增持。<br />\n<br />\n《路透》報導，波克夏海瑟威表示，其全資子公司National Indemnity Company持有這5家公司的股份，計劃長期持有，並可能將持股比例增至最高9.9%。<br />\n<br />\n巴菲特發表聲明稱：「我很高興波克夏海瑟威能參與日本的未來。這5大商社在世界各地有很多合資企業，而且可能有更多的這種夥伴關係...我希望未來能有互惠互利的機會。」<br />\n<br />\n.......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3276651\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3276651&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoCNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=1e7e1d68\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3276651&h=5f4679cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3276651</a>"},{"pid":"6e0dcc48ab5685b62c4e91f35d6eb8908d9eddf9","tid":2181891,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T02:37:28.000Z","msg":"《日經新聞》指出，這是巴菲特首次大量持有在日股上市的個股。消息促使5大商社股價狂飆，丸紅大漲12.39％，伊藤忠商事則漲5.11％、刷新10年來股價新高。<br />\n<br />\n《日經新聞》報導，巴菲特31日透過旗下子公司取得伊藤忠商事、三菱商事等5家日企約5%股權；報導也指出，這是巴菲特首次大量持有在日股上市的個股，他也在聲明中提及合作的可能性。<br />\n<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，巴菲特在過去12個月陸續在東京證交所買進上述公司的股權，他也在聲明中指出，最高可能將持股增加至9.9%，但也說明若沒有經過對方公司的董事會同意下，不會買進更多持股。<br />\n<br />\n巴菲特在聲明指出，很高興能有機會參與到日本5大商社的未來，並指出上述5大商社在全球各地都有合資事業，將來盼有機會進行合作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3276702\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3276702&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoCNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=67bfed79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3276702&h=4e4f8af4\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3276702</a>"},{"pid":"4686c5b8b0e68922c4817b72735d54a712e824a4","tid":2181891,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T02:39:14.000Z","msg":"睇落老左好多"},{"pid":"633812110a16972dfb82e5d874bece2adfcc2cbf","tid":2181891,"uid":73095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4686c5b8b0e68922c4817b72735d54a712e824a4","tid":2181891,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T02:39:14.000Z","msg":"睇落老左好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T02:49:31.000Z","msg":"90 碎啦"},{"pid":"c8e0d1a7cbeea5aa9246fb91b22ab4498ad01103","tid":2181891,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T03:07:45.000Z","msg":"廢佬入軍工業<br />\n睇黎準備開波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e203516e2e1d99a763cfda2bd67b32ff70eda38","tid":2181891,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T03:14:10.000Z","msg":"OK BOOMER<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d5a0ef958122c2f7c05ed8c3aa3d99f3c9051a","tid":2181891,"uid":43133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T04:16:45.000Z","msg":"竟然係日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2937c43a01e68d827be5369b9940569d0f1eb51c","tid":2181891,"uid":75823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T04:18:45.000Z","msg":"真係買起日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc93ff4619fa723bdad84a5bccc5f1c9dbd44254","tid":2181891,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T04:20:04.000